import * as React from 'react';

    // bgcolor: 'background.paper'

                variant="caption"
                color="#757575"
              >
                just now

        </ListItemButton>
        <Divider component="li" />

                variant="caption"

                7 minutes ago

        </ListItemButton>
        <Divider component="li" />

        <ListItemButton sx={{display: 'block', padding: '10px 20px'}}>
        <Typography
                component="span"
                variant="caption"
                color="#757575"

                iMAC적응기(1) 아이맥을 사다!

                sx={{display: 'block' }}

                variant="caption"
                color="#757575"
